:markdown
  The ``.invisible-font`` mixin can be used to text that you still need to keep
  in the DOM. Be aware, that it sets the font-size to 0 and makes it
  transparent, but the containing element might still affect your layout.

.highlight
  pre.highlight__listing.hljs
    code.less
      :highlight
        .invisible-font();
